      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Troublemaking Trio Pt. 2",
        "Client": "Elder Ranger",
        "Description": "Could be my imagination,\r\nbut the monsters of the Shrine\r\nRuins look spooked these days.\r\nI asked around, and a trio of\r\ntroublemaking monsters seem\r\nto be the culprits. Think you\r\ncan go check it out?",
        "Target": "Hunt all target monsters",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Trio infernal, partie 2",
        "Client": "Ranger ancien",
        "Description": "Je me fais peut-\u00EAtre des id\u00E9es,\r\nmais les monstres du Temple\r\noubli\u00E9 ont l\u0027air effray\u00E9s.\r\nIl semblerait que les responsables\r\nsoient trois monstres en\r\nfurie. Tu pourrais aller voir \u00E7a ?",
        "Target": "Chasser tous les monstres",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Teppisti alle Rovine sacre",
        "Client": "Ranger anziano",
        "Description": "Potrei averlo immaginato, ma\r\ni mostri delle Rovine sacre\r\nhanno un aspetto inquietante\r\nultimamente. Ho chiesto in giro\r\ne pare sia colpa di tre mostri\r\nfuriosi. Puoi andare a dare\r\nun\u0027occhiata?",
        "Target": "Caccia tutti i mostri assegnati",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Trio der St\u00F6renfriede II",
        "Client": "\u00C4ltester Waldh\u00FCter",
        "Description": "K\u00F6nnte meine Einbildung sein,\r\naber die Monster in den Heiligen\r\nRuinen scheinen Angst zu haben.\r\nIch habe mich umgeh\u00F6rt, und der\r\nGrund scheint ein Monster-Trio\r\nzu sein. K\u00F6nntest du dir das mal\r\nansehen?",
        "Target": "Erjage alle Zielmonster.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Tr\u00EDo de alborotadores, 2.\u00AA parte",
        "Client": "Forestal anciano",
        "Description": "Ser\u00E1 mi imaginaci\u00F3n, pero los\r\nmonstruos del Templo olvidado\r\nparecen asustados. Por lo\r\nvisto, los culpables son tres\r\nmonstruos problem\u00E1ticos.\r\n\u00BFPodr\u00EDas ir a echar un vistazo?",
        "Target": "Caza todos los objetivos",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u0425\u0443\u043B\u0438\u0433\u0430\u043D\u044B \u0432 \u0420\u0443\u0438\u043D\u0430\u0445 \u0441\u0432\u044F\u0442\u0438\u043B\u0438\u0449\u0430",
